<topic class="popup" template="Popup" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../../../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">Class Diagram Tool</title>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Popup Heading"><text styleclass="Popup Heading" translate="true">Class Diagram Tool</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Popup Heading"><table rowcount="1" colcount="2" style="cell-padding:0px; cell-spacing:0px; border-width:0px; cell-border-width:0px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:99px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Heading"><image src="Class Diagram.png" align="left" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:214px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Opens a </text><text styleclass="Program Feature" translate="true">Class Diagram</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> onto the entire class hierarchy present in the image. </text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Double-clicking a class in the hierarchy will open a browser onto that class. The </text><text styleclass="Program Feature" translate="true">Class Browser</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="Program Feature" translate="true">System Browser</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> also contain </text><text styleclass="Program Feature" translate="true">Class Diagram</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> plug-ins that display the local hierarchy diagram for the class currently being browsed.</text></para>
  </body>
</topic>
